name: Fleeting Phrases
description:
A series of six limited edition letterpressed posters celebrating phrases that strangers said which brought a smile. Loveable strangers met across South London in 2010/2011. 

20 limited edition prints of each poster, printed using fluro colours in letterpress on Zerkall Smooth 145gsm paper.

Each poster is £30 but sold as a complete series of 6 for £150. If you would like to buy an individual poster, please send me a personal e-mail.
